.Dd June 29, 2017
.Dt BL-COLUMN_NOGROFF 1
.Os OpenBSD
.Sh NAME
.Nm Bl-column_nogroff
.Nd column lists mishandled by groff
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Item macro without arguments:
.Bl -column "first column" "second column"
.It
text
.No macro Ta after tab
.El
.Pp
Tab macro at the beginning of a line:
.Bl -column "aa" "bb"
.It aa
.Ta bb
.El
